Package: dump1090
Architecture: armhf
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, net-tools
Description: ADS-B Ground Station System for RTL-SDR
 Networked Aviation Mode S / ADS-B decoder/translator with RTL-SDR software
 defined radio USB device support plus piaware, software to forward
 Mode S / ADS-B messages to FlightAware over a compressed, encrypted
 TLS connection.
 .
 Includes a mini-webserver that you can access to see aircraft in the vicinity
 of your receiver.
 .
 t automatically shares data with FlightAware and can be used/configured
 to share messages with other services.
